Class SumoAmbassador

    LibSumoAmbassador, SumoGuiAmbassador
    public class SumoAmbassador
extends AbstractSumoAmbassador
    Implementation of a AbstractSumoAmbassador for the traffic simulator SUMO. It allows to control the progress of the traffic simulation and publishes VehicleUpdates.
    See Also:
    FederateAmbassador, VehicleUpdates
